OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,6,Fmoving southeastwards on Tuesday. This
OL,7,Ffollowed on Wednesday and Thursday by
OL,8,Fsunshine and showers, heavy and
OL,9,Fthundery at times. Rather cool and
OL,10,Foften breezy. Further overnight frosts.
